              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-938A020B-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">Upon an Eye, inscribed to the R<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> Hon<hi rend="superscript">bl</hi> the Lady \Carteret By  Delany D.D.F.T.C. <hi rend="italics">overwriting</hi> by D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> D\</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-938A020B-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-938A020B-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-938A020B-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-938A020B-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-938A020B-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-938A020B-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-1" n="1">I reach all things near me &amp; far off to boot</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-2" n="2">Without stretching a finger or stirring a foot</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-3" n="3">I take them all in too, to add to y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>- wonder</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-4" n="4">Tho many &amp; various, &amp; large &amp; asunder</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-5" n="5">Without justling or Crowding they pass Side by Side</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-6" n="6">Through a wonderfull wicket not half an inch wide</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-7" n="7">Then I lodge them at ease in a very large Store</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-8" n="8">Of no heath or lenth with a thousand things more</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-9" n="9">All this I can do without witchcraft or Charm</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-10" n="10">Tho sometimes they Say I bewitch &amp; do harm</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-11" n="11">Tho cold I inflame &amp; tho quiet invade</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-12" n="12">And nothing can shield f<hi rend="superscript">m</hi>- my Spell but a Shade</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-13" n="13">A Thief that has rob'd you \or done y<hi rend="superscript">uÌ£</hi> <hi rend="italics">above line</hi>\ disgrace</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-14" n="14">In Magical Mirrour I'll shew you his face</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-15" n="15">Nay if you'll believe what the Poets have said</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-16" n="16">They tell you I kill &amp; call back the dead</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-17" n="17">Like Conjurers safe in my Circle I dwell</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-18" n="18">I love to look black too, it heightens my Spell</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-19" n="19">Thou my Magick is mighty in every hue</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-938A020B-line-20" n="20">Who sees all my power must see it in <hi rend="underlined">you</hi></l>
          </lg>
        </div>
